				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Excellent essay <em>and</em> story, thanks!</p>
<p>You go pretty far on several axes: including maybe-disorders like being trans, allowing brain tweaks and leaving all decisions up to the parents.</p>
<p>So, would tweaks like lifelong-obedience-to-parents also be OK? For some parents, misbehaving kids and wayward adult children seem to be major causes of distress.</p>
<p id="comment-like-2371" data-liked=comment-not-liked class="comment-likes comment-not-liked"><a href="https://carcinisation.com/2015/04/03/have-mercy/?like_comment=2371&#038;_wpnonce=576ebcb0ad" class="comment-like-link needs-login" rel="nofollow" data-blog="71183487"><span>Like</span></a><span id="comment-like-count-2371" class="comment-like-feedback">Like</span></p>
