				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Reblogged this on <a href="http://josephratliff.net/2015/05/01/have-mercy/" rel="nofollow">The Ratliff Notepad</a>.</p>
<p id="comment-like-2461" data-liked=comment-not-liked class="comment-likes comment-not-liked"><a href="https://carcinisation.com/2015/04/03/have-mercy/?like_comment=2461&#038;_wpnonce=e51ced0a94" class="comment-like-link needs-login" rel="nofollow" data-blog="71183487"><span>Like</span></a><span id="comment-like-count-2461" class="comment-like-feedback">Like</span></p>
