				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/2015/04/03/have-mercy/?like_comment=2382&#038;_wpnonce=a3319f12cf&#038;replytocom=2461#respond' data-commentid="2461" data-postid="447" data-belowelement="div-comment-2461" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Joseph Ratliff'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
